\fs29 <p>If this strikes you as unreasonable or ridiculous, go check out the TikTok account for sutherlandphys, operated by oneChris Sutherland, a physics professor at the University of Southern California who has two million followers and who makes videos with captions like \'93Im the type of professor to pretend I dont understand your question just so I dont have to answer.\'94 He even has his own merch line, featuring hoodies and tees that look like university apparel and have a slogan that reads sutherlandphysest. 2020.</p>\
